This makes the data actionable across marketing and sales, improving efficiency and closing rates.

9. Alignment with ABM and Lead Generation Goals

Intent data is only as impactful as its alignment with your demand generation strategy. Whether you’re running full-funnel programs or targeted ABM initiatives, the provider must support personalized messaging, audience segmentation, and targeted campaigns.

Look for providers offering:

